@Morten Irgens in reference to your recent twitter post: "I am looking forward to comprehensive discussions of how a European public private partnership in AI best can be constructed".
Please see the following document on "From Research to Market:What the EU can learn from the USA?"
https://escholarship.org/uc/item/7zp5b130
I think you will find it useful on crafting public private sector partnerships.
This is a very useful report. Thank you very much for bringing it to my attention
